race.comment: SHORTY BOY (6) boasts a strong record this journey with six wins and three minors from 16 tries. Scored by 1.75 lengths last time (25.24) in a Grade 4/5 over 450m at Warrnambool. Looks well placed and should feature. HUNTERVIEW LAD (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (24.47) at Sale. Has a good record at this journey. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Bold showing expected. MR. THOMAS (5) has a strong record this trip with seven wins and five placings from 16 starts. Missed the frame latest (26.26) when fifth over 460m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Looks well placed here and among the chances. QILIN BALE (8) is one of the chances after collecting a minor prize last time. Something for the Multiples: MR. THOMAS (5)
